---

---

<section class="hero">
	<div class="hero-container">
		<div class="hero-left">
			<h1>From roots<br>to remembrance —<br>unlock your<br>true purpose</h1>
			<p class="intro">
				Sáamaka Soul is a spiritual and holistic lifestyle company that integrates coaching and clothing to help people reconnect with their true selves.
			</p>
			<p class="description">
				Through one-on-one sessions, I guide men and women toward their deepest core, enabling them to rediscover their inner strength and purpose. In addition, I offer exclusive black T-shirts with powerful, spiritual messages - designed as tangible extensions of the coaching experience.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="hero-right">
			<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531746020798-e6953c6e8e04?w=600&h=800&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="Portrait" />
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		background-color: #000000;
		padding: 3rem 4rem;
	}

	.hero-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
		gap: 2rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.hero-right {
		justify-self: end;
	}

	.hero-right img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 350px;
		height: auto;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.15;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.intro {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.description {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.hero-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.hero-left {
			order: 2;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.hero-right {
			order: 1;
			justify-self: center;
		}

		.hero-right img {
			max-width: 250px;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>
